yetst volt ikh aykh gevolt fregn nokh a frage.

198
00:08:59,455 --> 00:09:00,208
yo.

199
00:09:01,227 --> 00:09:03,448
loyt dem vos ir hot dertseylt

200
00:09:05,513 --> 00:09:07,836
iz ayer yetstike froy

201
00:09:08,010 --> 00:09:10,636
a ibergelebte, un ir zent a ibergelebte.

202
00:09:08,820 --> 00:09:11,008
ibergelebt, iber- yo.

203
00:09:12,567 --> 00:09:13,686
tsi hot ir

204
00:09:13,686 --> 00:09:17,677
di ale yorn, ven ir, ven d-, ven ayer tokhter is oyfgevaksn,

205
00:09:17,686 --> 00:09:22,774
hot zi zikh gefregt, far mir, dertseylt di kinde- di tokhter, di eyniklekh, vos me hot als adurkhgemakht?

206
00:09:20,852 --> 00:09:21,622
yo.

207
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:26,634
nu, koydem, dos ershte mol nisht, ho'mir nisht gevolt dertseyln.

208
00:09:26,758 --> 00:09:29,067
vayl me hot geklert, s'iz genug in undz

209
00:09:29,067 --> 00:09:32,029
kh'hob mikh aleyn nisht gevolt dermanen, vayl ikh zog nokh, afile haynt,

210
00:09:32,029 --> 00:09:36,129
kler ikh a sakh mol az s'iz gornisht emes, s'iz nisht meglekh az ikh zol zayn do.

211
00:09:36,129 --> 00:09:37,419
ho'mir nisht gevolt dertseyln,

212
00:09:37,452 --> 00:09:40,000
ober nokh dem hobn di eyniklekh ongehoybn fregn,

213
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,613
nisht di tokhter, nor di eyniklekh,

214
00:09:41,613 --> 00:09:43,968
azoy arum az me ho'mir dertseylt

215
00:09:43,968 --> 00:09:46,220
far di tokhter un far di eyniklekh, zey veysn

216
00:09:46,220 --> 00:09:47,613
aldings, genoy,

217
00:09:47,613 --> 00:09:49,736
vos s'iz geshen un vi azoy s'iz geshen.

218
00:09:49,422 --> 00:09:52,217
nokh a kurtse frage, mit ayer erloybenish.

219
00:09:50,805 --> 00:09:51,659
yo.

220
00:09:52,645 --> 00:09:55,727
b-, loyt dem vos, di ale tsores vos ir hot adurkhgemakht,

221
00:09:53,944 --> 00:09:57,498
yo, yo, ikh, ikh vil aykh epes dertseyln nokh a zakh.

222
00:09:56,170 --> 00:09:57,870
bite. bite.

223
00:09:57,673 --> 00:09:58,733
iz,

224
00:09:58,733 --> 00:10:01,193
ikh vil aykh dertseyln, in shaykhes mit dem,

225
00:10:01,193 --> 00:10:05,138
ershtn CHALOM mayne, mitn kholem, vil ikh aykh dertseyln,

226
00:10:05,138 --> 00:10:07,888
az nokh dem vi ikh hob getrofn di tsveyte

227
00:10:07,888 --> 00:10:10,458
in Satu-Mare ven ikh bin geforn zi zukhn,

228
00:10:10,650 --> 00:10:12,225
hot zi mir dertseylt

229
00:10:12,225 --> 00:10:16,011
"du veyst," zogt zi, "dem ershtn oyf der nakht, fraytog oyf der nakht,"

230
00:10:16,050 --> 00:10:22,726
"in Oyshvits, oyf dey pritshn ven me hot zikh nisht gekent rurn, hob ikh gekholemt a tayern kholem."

231
00:10:22,733 --> 00:10:29,429
"in der kholem," zogt zi, "hot mikh gehaltn biz ende. ikh hob gekholemt ikh zits bay mayn tatn baym tish,"

232
00:10:29,429 --> 00:10:33,023
"un der tate shnaydt fun di groyse khale far yedn,"

233
00:10:33,023 --> 00:10:41,267
"un s'iz ales azoy sheyn un voyl," zogt zi, "un kh'hob dervekt in Oyshvits oyfn pritshn." deys hob ikh gevolt dertseyln fun ir. un, nokh a kholem hot zi dertseylt.

234
00:10:41,267 --> 00:10:43,714
zi iz bafrayt gevorn in THERESIENSTADT.

235
00:10:43,714 --> 00:10:46,993
deys iz geven im nayntn ⟨marts⟩, shpeter vu ikh.

236
00:10:47,050 --> 00:10:49,401
un zi iz arayngefaln in a tifus.

237
00:10:49,401 --> 00:10:51,330
vi azoy iz zi arayngefaln in a tifus?

238
00:10:51,387 --> 00:10:54,226
di shvegerins ire zenen bald dem andern tog geganen

239
00:10:54,226 --> 00:10:56,678
organizirn, dort hot men gezogt organizirn,

240
00:10:56,774 --> 00:10:58,581
broyt un fleysh, un vu me hot gekent,

241
00:10:58,581 --> 00:11:00,484
zi hot getrofn ergets in a keler

242
00:11:00,504 --> 00:11:03,634
kartofl, mit shinke. shinke.

243
00:11:03,634 --> 00:11:07,411
un zi hot gebrengt, un zi hot opgekokht a groysn top shinke mit kartofl.

244
00:11:07,671 --> 00:11:09,094
un mayne

245
00:11:09,094 --> 00:11:13,962
hot oykh gegesn, vayl m'iz dokh hungerik geven dortn, un s'iz ir gekumen arayn in moyl, un se hot ir geglitsht,

246
00:11:13,962 --> 00:11:16,721
un zi hot zikh zeyer fargroylt, zi hot gezen az dos iz shinke.

247
00:11:16,721 --> 00:11:19,033
fun dem fargroyl iz zi arayngefaln in tifus.

248
00:11:19,033 --> 00:11:22,244
un s'iz geven dort akht, tsen tog tifus in bet.

249
00:11:22,403 --> 00:11:26,829
un befor mit tsvey tog heyder s'iz geven der krizis bayn ir,

250
00:11:26,829 --> 00:11:33,385
hot zi mir dertseylt, iz arayngekumen a rusisher dokter, un tsvey shvester, un zey hobn gehat in di hent aza ⟨CHOVERET⟩

251
00:11:33,385 --> 00:11:43,662
un zey hobn ongehoybn oyftsushraybn, vayl s'iz geven di ende fun di tifusnikes dortn, vayl fun deye iz veynik oyfgeshtanen. me hot zi gefregt ver zi iz fun der heym, oyb zi hot nokh emetsn in der velt, az

252
00:11:43,662 --> 00:11:47,239
m'hot ir nisht gezogt far vos, nor me zol kenen nokh dem tsu visn gebn.

253
00:11:47,239 --> 00:11:48,164
zogt zi,

254
00:11:48,778 --> 00:11:51,100
di elefte nakht fun tifus,

255
00:11:51,141 --> 00:11:53,160
zogt zi, zi iz gelegn in a hits,

256
00:11:54,887 --> 00:11:57,209
se hot zikh gegosn dos vaser fun ir,

257
00:11:57,739 --> 00:11:59,488
zi hot nisht gevust fun zikh.

258
00:11:59,646 --> 00:12:01,496
zogt zi, plutsem kholemt zi

259
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:04,671
az der ⟨rabay⟩ kumt un shrayt,

260
00:12:04,671 --> 00:12:10,963
"du zest nisht, Perl, gey arop funem RAKEVET! funem PASEY RAKEVET! der RAKEVET kumt er vet dikh iberforn."

261
00:12:11,644 --> 00:12:17,865
zogt zi, "un azoy shrayendik iz er tsugekumen un hot mikh ongekhapt un hot mikh aropgeshlept. demolt hob ikh mikh dervekt."

262
00:12:18,158 --> 00:12:22,860
"s'iz lebn mir geshtanen ACHOT, a rusishe, un zi hot mir gegebn HAZRAKAH."

263
00:12:23,187 --> 00:12:25,121
un demolt iz ir beser gevorn.

264
00:12:25,279 --> 00:12:31,365
deys iz khaloymes, me zogt me gleybt nisht in khaloymes, ober epes iz in dem. deys hob ikh gevolt tsugebn.

265
00:12:31,067 --> 00:12:33,676
yetst hob ikh aykh gevolt fregn nokh a kurtse frage.

266
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:33,947
yo.

267
00:12:34,611 --> 00:12:38,807
nokh dem vi ir hot alts dertseylt vos ir hot alts adurkhgemakht, oyb ir kukt

268
00:12:36,265 --> 00:12:37,119
yo.

269
00:12:38,931 --> 00:12:41,119
tsurik, vos se hot alts pasirt,

270
00:12:39,825 --> 00:12:40,764
yo.

271
00:12:41,310 --> 00:12:43,683
vi hot er gevirkt oyf ayer lebn?

272
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:49,517
un zo- nu zog ikh dokh aykh, deys hot gevirkt oyf farshidene zakhn.

273
00:12:44,193 --> 00:12:46,483
di ale tsores. bizn hayntikn tog.

274
00:12:49,517 --> 00:12:53,117
koydem hot gevirkt oyf dem, az se kumt a normale mentsh oyf a plats,

275
00:12:53,224 --> 00:12:56,086
vu er bakumt a tog a bisele shvarts vaser,

276
00:12:56,177 --> 00:12:57,470
mit efsher

277
00:12:57,662 --> 00:12:59,900
ikh veys, efsher tsvey hundert gram

278
00:12:59,991 --> 00:13:02,468
broyt, vos dos iz fun a hart breytl.

279
00:13:02,468 --> 00:13:05,182
hot gevirkt mayne ale tsen demoltsdike

280
00:13:05,222 --> 00:13:06,971
zenen aroysgefaln.

281
00:13:07,230 --> 00:13:09,232
ikh bin krank gevorn oyfn mogn.

282
00:13:09,525 --> 00:13:11,375
biz im hayntikn tog.

283
00:13:11,500 --> 00:13:14,433
un, ikh ken aykh zogn dem emes,

284
00:13:14,433 --> 00:13:16,580
vi azoy ikh hob dos dertseylt far aykh veys ikh nisht,

285
00:13:16,580 --> 00:13:18,323
vayl ikh zog az ikh bin nisht normal.

286
00:13:18,323 --> 00:13:21,000
vayl oyb a mentsh ken fun Oyshvits aroyskumen

287
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,936
un hern mit zayne oyern

288
00:13:22,936 --> 00:13:26,546
az mayn froy, un kinder, un muter geyen in flamen,

289
00:13:27,025 --> 00:13:28,571
ken nisht zayn klor.

290
00:13:28,965 --> 00:13:30,438
zog ikh oyf mir.

291
00:13:30,438 --> 00:13:31,848
ikh veys nisht andere,

292
00:13:31,848 --> 00:13:34,421
azoy gevirkt es, un se virkt biz haynt,

293
00:13:34,421 --> 00:13:37,906
vayl ikh hob azoy fil khaloymes gehat, vos ikh shtey oyf in der fri,

294
00:13:37,906 --> 00:13:40,168
gist zikh dos vaser fun mir, ikh veys nisht far vos,

295
00:13:40,168 --> 00:13:43,071
vayl ikh bahalt mikh far di S.S., ikh veys nisht vos tsu ton.

296
00:13:44,288 --> 00:13:47,724
yetst volt ikh aykh gevolt fregn, rikhtik, nisht keyn frage,

297
00:13:47,427 --> 00:13:48,231
yo.

298
00:13:48,118 --> 00:13:49,968
nor ven ven ikh volt aykh gezogt

299
00:13:50,430 --> 00:13:56,533
ven ir darft shikn a telegram tsu di tsukumftike doyres, tsu di doyre-doyres, in der tsukumft,

300
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,208
yo.

301
00:13:54,868 --> 00:13:55,706
yo.

302
00:13:56,067 --> 00:13:56,888
yo.

303
00:13:56,792 --> 00:14:01,443
vos far a eytse volt ir zey gegebn alts, nokh dem vos ir hot alts adurkhgemakht?

304
00:14:00,623 --> 00:14:01,539
yo.

305
00:14:01,539 --> 00:14:03,682
ikh het gegebn eyn eytse.

306
00:14:03,682 --> 00:14:06,202
in meynstn teyl farn yidishn folk.

307
00:14:06,597 --> 00:14:08,835
az vu se gefint zikh eyner,

308
00:14:09,060 --> 00:14:10,980
un iber hoypt di yugntlekhe,

309
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:12,795
hobn zey eyn plats

310
00:14:12,795 --> 00:14:14,837
dos iz in ERETZ-YISRAEL.

311
00:14:14,837 --> 00:14:17,695
un ergets in der velt veln zey deys nisht hobn.

312
00:14:17,751 --> 00:14:21,849
vayl undz ho'mir oykh gehat gute tsaytn, me hot gemeynt az keyn besers iz nisht do.

313
00:14:21,849 --> 00:14:24,096
ober leyder sof iz geven nisht gut.

314
00:14:24,139 --> 00:14:27,074
un azoy iz iberal mit di best fraynt vos me hot.

315
00:14:27,107 --> 00:14:29,816
ven se kumt tsum sof iz nisht do keyn fraynt.

316
00:14:29,889 --> 00:14:32,595
iz di beste zakh vos ikh vintsh far ale yidn,

317
00:14:32,871 --> 00:14:35,987
meyle, di kristn veln undz helfn, s'iz do eyntsele vos zenen

318
00:14:36,043 --> 00:14:39,044
dey vos zey geyen in Yad-Vashem, dos zenen eyntsele,

319
00:14:39,044 --> 00:14:41,623
ober di yidn hobn nisht keyn ander plats

320
00:14:41,623 --> 00:14:43,462
afile ven zey shepn gold,

321
00:14:43,462 --> 00:14:45,849
zoln zey visn az deys iz nor tsaytvaylik.

322
00:14:45,849 --> 00:14:47,507
ober leoylom-habe,

323
00:14:47,507 --> 00:14:50,465
iz undzer erd do. do, do.

324
00:14:52,176 --> 00:14:55,292
s'iz nokh epes vos ir hot gevolt tsugebn tsu ayer SIPUR?

325
00:14:55,652 --> 00:14:57,285
vos ir hot zikh epes dermant

326
00:14:57,285 --> 00:14:58,295
spetsyel?

327
00:14:58,588 --> 00:15:01,366
vayl tomer nisht geyen mir ariber tsu di...

328
00:15:00,529 --> 00:15:02,986
yo. ikh vel aykh zogn.

329
00:15:02,993 --> 00:15:04,455
kh'hob mikh dermant

330
00:15:04,596 --> 00:15:05,748
az,

331
00:15:05,748 --> 00:15:07,790
loyt vi do in land firt zikh,

332
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:10,355
s'iz leyder az undz tsvishn undz,

333
00:15:10,355 --> 00:15:11,812
ho'mir nisht keyn sholem.

334
00:15:11,886 --> 00:15:14,701
deys iz der vikhtikster prat, iber alemen.

335
00:15:14,701 --> 00:15:17,283
ven se het geven az eyn yid mitn andern,

336
00:15:17,283 --> 00:15:19,637
tsi er iz a CHILONI, tsi er iz a DAATI,

337
00:15:19,637 --> 00:15:21,012
het geven fareynikt,

338
00:15:21,012 --> 00:15:22,916
het andersh geven bayn undz in land.

339
00:15:23,091 --> 00:15:29,987
deys eyne bet ikh got ikh zol nokh kenen khotsh azoy fil lebn, az deys zol zayn fareynikt, vet mayn harts zayn oyfn plats.

340
00:15:30,027 --> 00:15:31,590
vayl ikh zog aykh,

341
00:15:31,748 --> 00:15:36,022
az mayn lebn iz far mayn tokhter, un far di tsvey eyniklekh vos ikh ze.

342
00:15:36,022 --> 00:15:37,355
ikh ze zey,

343
00:15:37,355 --> 00:15:39,949
deys git mir tsu yedn tog mut.

344
00:15:39,949 --> 00:15:44,634
deys hob ikh gevolt tsugebn.

345
00:15:40,843 --> 00:15:44,532
ikh hob aykh gevolt danken far dem vikhtikn teyl vos ir dertseylt.

346
00:15:44,775 --> 00:15:45,933
TODA RABA

347
00:15:44,978 --> 00:15:48,279
veln mir ariber geyn yetst oyf dem teyl fun di fotografyes.

348
00:15:53,567 --> 00:16:01,998
her Meyir, yetst geyen mir ariber tsu dem teyl fun di bilder. zayt azoy gut, zogt mir fun vanet hot ir di bilder fun der heym, di historishe bilder?

349
00:16:01,718 --> 00:16:05,475
deys historishe bild, dem SABA un di SAVTA,

350
00:16:05,548 --> 00:16:07,334
hob ikh gehat a mume

351
00:16:07,334 --> 00:16:20,477
deys heyst mayn mame's a shvester, un zi hot gevoynt do in ERETZ-YISRAEL. un zi hot gehat deys bild fun far di milkhome. azoy bin ikh gekumen, mit ir zun, hot es mir gebrengt, a kleyn bildele, un ikh hob es fargresert.

352
00:16:19,977 --> 00:16:22,367
verzhe iz oyfn bild, zogt mir di nemen.

353
00:16:21,478 --> 00:16:28,070
oyf dem bild, di nemen heyst Khane heyst di SAVTA, un Shmuel heyst der SABA, hot geheysn.

354
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:29,960
ven hobn zey geshtorbn?

355
00:16:29,190 --> 00:16:30,972
zey zenen geshtorbn...

356
00:16:30,253 --> 00:16:31,833
zikhroynem livrokhe?

357
00:16:31,435 --> 00:16:34,281
 der SABA iz geshtorbn

358
00:16:34,371 --> 00:16:36,789
in in nayn im draysiker yor.

359
00:16:36,789 --> 00:16:40,912
un di SAVTA iz geshtorbn in in

360
00:16:42,319 --> 00:16:44,118
dray un fertsiker yor.

361
00:16:47,196 --> 00:16:51,881
vi arum hot ir di andere bilder fun far ⟨di krig⟩, un ayer froy's bilder?

362
00:16:52,022 --> 00:16:53,349
deys bild

363
00:16:53,355 --> 00:16:54,862
ho'mir undz bakumen

364
00:16:54,862 --> 00:16:59,090
fun der shvegerin, fun mayn froy's a shvester, i fun der ershter, i fun der tsveyter,

365
00:16:59,090 --> 00:17:01,123
ho'mir bakumen deys in MEXICO.

366
00:17:01,123 --> 00:17:05,516
zi hot undz gegebn deys, men hot gemakht a kopye, un me hot gebrengt dos bild aheym.

367
00:17:05,016 --> 00:17:06,832
un oykh ire bilder.

368
00:17:06,196 --> 00:17:07,118
oykh ir bilder.

369
00:17:07,159 --> 00:17:08,705
verzhe iz oyfn bild?

370
00:17:08,204 --> 00:17:11,033
oyfn bild bin ikh un mayn ershte froy.

371
00:17:10,534 --> 00:17:12,165
velkhe yor iz dos?

372
00:17:11,597 --> 00:17:13,464
deys iz draysiker yor.

373
00:17:13,335 --> 00:17:15,657
vi hot geheysn ayer ershte froy?

374
00:17:15,022 --> 00:17:16,011
Helen.

375
00:17:15,900 --> 00:17:17,666
un vos hot mir ir pasirt?

376
00:17:18,212 --> 00:17:21,615
vos heyst vos hot mit ir pasirt, mit di kinder, in Oyshvits umgekumen!

377
00:17:22,363 --> 00:17:24,601
vi hobn geheysn ayere kinder, gedenkt ir?

378
00:17:24,102 --> 00:17:25,277
yo, yo,

379
00:17:24,777 --> 00:17:26,205
UNK

380
00:17:25,317 --> 00:17:26,391
Edit.

381
00:17:26,633 --> 00:17:27,760
Betsalel.

382
00:17:27,760 --> 00:17:31,756
nokh mayn foter. Nokh dem iz geven Reyzi, Malka.

383
00:17:35,593 --> 00:17:37,764
ver iz oyf dem bild, bite?

384
00:17:37,146 --> 00:17:41,325
oyf dem bild iz mayn gevezenem shver olev-hasholem,

385
00:17:41,162 --> 00:17:42,523
vi hot er geheysn?

386
00:17:42,208 --> 00:17:44,834
er hot geheysn Sruel-Mekhl.

387
00:17:45,448 --> 00:17:48,128
un ahintern, un dos andere

388
00:17:48,128 --> 00:17:50,347
iz di shtif-muter far mayn froy,

389
00:17:50,347 --> 00:17:52,631
un ahinter iz mayn froy, di tsveyte.

390
00:17:52,587 --> 00:17:56,040
vos hot pasirt mit di mentshn vos zenen oyfn bild, akhuts ayer froy?

391
00:17:55,253 --> 00:17:58,824
akhuts mayn froy zenen zey umgekumen in Oyshvits.

392
00:18:01,800 --> 00:18:02,638
bite.

393
00:18:03,792 --> 00:18:05,890
deys iz mayne shvoger.

394
00:18:05,890 --> 00:18:07,872
deys heyst dos iz a bruder

395
00:18:07,872 --> 00:18:11,880
gevezn far mayn froy, far di ershte un far di tsveyte.

396
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:14,096
er hot geheysn Meyer Ber.

397
00:18:14,777 --> 00:18:16,813
zi hot geheysn Khane.

398
00:18:17,123 --> 00:18:25,200
deys iz di froy vos zi iz geven UNK. zey zenen umgekumen mit di kinder in Oyshvits. zey hobn gehat...

399
